{
    "content": "<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">很久没玩</span>DOF<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">单机了，这次玩的时候被强化碎装备搞得有点不爽，于是又折腾了下</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">upgrade.etc</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">文件，得到了以下几点</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">增幅同理</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">：</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3037</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">是需求材料</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">ID</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3037</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">后一位（即</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">④</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）是材料需求数量</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3037</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">前第一二位（即</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">②③</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）组合决定装备强化失败是否降级或损坏，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">维持原等级，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">降级，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">损坏</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3037</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">前第三位（即</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">①</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）决定强化概率，计算方式为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(100000-X)/100000</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"290\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/09/10/image-20230910231634-1.png\" width=\"520\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">举例：</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">①75000 2 0 3037 120</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">表示该等级强化需求</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3037</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（无色小晶块）</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">120</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个，强化成功概率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，强化失败装备强化等级降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">级。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">②20000 2 2 3037 100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">表示该等级强化需求</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3037</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（无色小晶块）</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个，强化成功概率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">80%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，强化失败装备强化等级降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">级。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">③90000 3 0 3037 500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">表示该等级强化需求</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3037</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（无色小晶块）</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个，强化成功概率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，强化失败装备损坏。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">④1000 1 0 3242 1000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">表示该等级强化需求</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3037</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（矛盾的结晶体）</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">0<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个，强化成功概率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">99%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，强化失败装备维持原等级。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">自改强化增幅内容：</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">①</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">金币、材料需求提升至</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">倍</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">②</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">强化增幅失败时装备不会损坏</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">③</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">强化增幅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1-4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">级</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">100%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成功</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原版），</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">级后成功率为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">44%.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">④</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">从</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">级开始，每</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">级为保级等级，即</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4+3*N</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）等等级失败装备不掉级。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">⑤5+N*3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">级别失败时降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">级，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6+N*3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">级别失败时降</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">级。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"439\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/09/10/image-20230910231634-2.png\" width=\"642\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"391\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/09/10/image-20230910231634-3.png\" width=\"608\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">最后，感谢下各位大神制作分享的工具，我只想说一句，真</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">TM</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">好用！</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"background-color:#e74c3c\">最后附上文件下载链接</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"background-color:#e74c3c\">https://www.123pan.com/s/tJCtVv-QK5EH.html提取码:ibAy</span></span></span></p>\n",
